Robert P. Hughes's Biography




			Mr. Robert P. Hughes (principal financial and accounting officer) has served as our Senior Vice President, Finance and Risk Management since 2013. He had previously served as Vice President and Controller since joining Overstock in 2008. Mr. Hughes holds a bachelor's degree in Business Administration with an emphasis in Accounting and Finance from the University of California Berkeley, Haas School of Business, and is a certified public accountant (CA - inactive status).
		
