Our Attorneys



Robert P. Richards
 OF COUNSEL  (808) 526-9744 Ext. 111 
Mr. Richards graduated from the University of California at Berkley with a B.A. He received his J.D. from the University of California, Hastings College of Law. 
Mr. Richards specializes in insurance law, civil and trial practice, personal injury defense, premises liability, commercial transactions, construction litigation, professional malpractice and product defect. He provides expert analysis in the area of "standard of care" in litigation and "reasonableness and necessity" of fees in litigation. He is rated AV Pre-eminent by Martindale Hubbell and was selected one of the Top Lawyers in Hawaii by the Legal Network.



